# Runtime artifacts under <scenario>/.local/share/cctally/ are unexpected
# — the bin/cctally-update-test harness runs every scenario inside a
# per-run mktemp -d scratch root, so the in-tree fixture trees stay
# byte-stable. The patterns below scope ONLY to the per-scenario top-
# level <scenario>/.local/ tree (NOT the committed pre/.local/ trees,
# which seed the scratch HOME and may contain identically-named files
# like update-check.last-fetch).
*/.local/
